  "This schedule was created when Asset {0} was sold through Sales Invoice {1}.": "Bu \u00e7izelge, Varl\u0131k {0} '\u0131n Sat\u0131\u015f Faturas\u0131 {1} i\u00e7in iade edilmesiyle olu\u015fturuldu.",
  "This schedule was created when Asset {0} was updated after being split into new Asset {1}.": "Bu program, Varl\u0131k {0} yeni Varl\u0131k {1} olarak b\u00f6l\u00fcnd\u00fckten sonra g\u00fcncellendi\u011finde olu\u015fturulmu\u015ftur.",
  "This schedule was created when Asset {0}'s Asset Repair {1} was cancelled.": "Bu program, Varl\u0131k {0}'\u0131n Varl\u0131k Onar\u0131m\u0131 {1} iptal edildi\u011finde olu\u015fturuldu.",
  "This schedule was created when Asset {0}'s Asset Value Adjustment {1} was cancelled.": "Bu program, Varl\u0131k {0}'\u0131n Varl\u0131k Onar\u0131m\u0131 {1} iptal edildi\u011finde olu\u015fturuldu.",
  "This schedule was created when Asset {0}'s shifts were adjusted through Asset Shift Allocation {1}.": "Bu \u00e7izelge, Varl\u0131k {0} Varl\u0131k De\u011feri Ayarlamas\u0131 {1} arac\u0131l\u0131\u011f\u0131yla ayarland\u0131\u011f\u0131nda olu\u015fturulmu\u015ftur.",
  "This schedule was created when new Asset {0} was split from Asset {1}.": "Bu plan, Varl\u0131k {0} i\u00e7in Varl\u0131k Onar\u0131m\u0131 {1} ile onar\u0131ld\u0131\u011f\u0131 zaman olu\u015fturuldu.",
  "This section allows the user to set the Body and Closing text of the Dunning Letter for the Dunning Type based on language, which can be used in Print.": "Bu b\u00f6l\u00fcm, kullan\u0131c\u0131n\u0131n Yazd\u0131r'da kullan\u0131labilecek dile ba\u011fl\u0131 olarak \u0130htar Mektubunun G\u00f6vde ve Kapan\u0131\u015f metnini \u0130htar T\u00fcr\u00fc i\u00e7in ayarlamas\u0131na olanak tan\u0131r.",
  "This site is in read only mode, full functionality will be restored soon.": "Bu site salt okunur modundad\u0131r, yak\u0131nda t\u00fcm i\u015flevleri geri y\u00fcklenecektir.",
  "This site is running in developer mode. Any change made here will be updated in code.": "Bu site geli\u015ftirici modunda \u00e7al\u0131\u015f\u0131yor. Burada yap\u0131lan herhangi bir de\u011fi\u015fiklik kodda g\u00fcncellenecektir.",
  "This table is used to set details about the 'Item', 'Qty', 'Basic Rate', etc.": "Bu tablo, '\u00dcr\u00fcn', 'Miktar', 'Birim Fiyat' vb. ile ilgili ayr\u0131nt\u0131lar\u0131 ayarlamak i\u00e7in kullan\u0131l\u0131r.",
  "This title will be used as the title of the webpage as well as in meta tags": "Bu ba\u015fl\u0131k, web sayfas\u0131n\u0131n ba\u015fl\u0131\u011f\u0131 ve meta etiketlerinde kullan\u0131lacakt\u0131r",
  "This tool helps you to update or fix the quantity and valuation of stock in the system. It is typically used to synchronise the system values and what actually exists in your warehouses.": "Bu ara\u00e7, sistemdeki stok miktar\u0131n\u0131 ve de\u011ferlemesini g\u00fcncellemenize veya d\u00fczeltmenize yard\u0131mc\u0131 olur. Genellikle sistem de\u011ferlerini ve depolar\u0131n\u0131zda ger\u00e7ekte var olanlar\u0131 senkronize etmek i\u00e7in kullan\u0131l\u0131r.",
  "This topic is already added to the existing courses": "Bu konu zaten mevcut kurslara eklendi",
  "This value is updated in the Default Sales Price List.": "Bu de\u011fer Varsay\u0131lan Sat\u0131\u015f Fiyat\u0131 Listesinde g\u00fcncellenir.",
